values.value: SELECT ID, Name , Portal_Title__c FROM Campaign WHERE (NOT Name LIKE '%test%') AND Portal_Title__c != null AND ((Event_Type__c LIKE '%motoring%') OR (Status IN ('Approved for portal and invites', 'Completed') AND (Event_Type__c IN ('Family Camp', 'Family Fun Day', 'Family Respite', 'Junior Camp', 'Middle Camp', 'Mini Camp', 'Multi Age Group Camp', 'Virtual Camp')AND StartDate >= LAST_N_DAYS:14 AND StartDate <= NEXT_N_DAYS:14)))
